== About me
I received the B.S. degree in Software Engineering (Supervisor: Professor [https://gd.dlnu.edu.cn/dsxx/dzxx/102914.htm Xiaodong Duan]) from [https://www.dlnu.edu.cn/comd/index.htm College of Computer Science and Engineering], [https://new.dlnu.edu.cn/ Dalian Minzu University],
the M.S. degree in Computer Technology (Supervisor: Professor Guanyu Li) from [http://ist.dlmu.edu.cn/, Information Science and Technology College], [http://www.dlmu.edu.cn/ Dalian Maritime University], and the Ph.D. degree in Control Theory and Control Engineering (Supervisor: Professors [http://faculty.dlut.edu.cn/2005011016/zh_CN/index.htm Xiaodong Liu] and [https://gd.dlnu.edu.cn/dsxx/dzxx/102914.htm Xiaodong Duan]) from [http://scse.dlut.edu.cn/ School of Control Science and Engineering], [http://ee.dlut.edu.cn/, Faculty of Electronic Information and Electrical Engineering], [https://www.dlut.edu.cn/ Dalian University of Technology] in 2012, 2014, and 2018, respectively.
My research interests include axiomatic fuzzy set, deep fuzzy system, clinical data mining and personality computing. I am a member of China Computer Federation (CCF).
